Package soot.jimple.infoflow.data.pathBuilders

Class BatchPathBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.jimple.infoflow.data.pathBuilders.AbstractAbstractionPathBuilder
      • soot.jimple.infoflow.data.pathBuilders.BatchPathBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAbstractionPathBuilder, IMemoryBoundedSolver
    public class BatchPathBuilder
extends AbstractAbstractionPathBuilder
    Path builder that forwards all its requests to another path builder in batches. This builder waits for each batch to complete before submitting another batch. Use this path builder to reduce the memory consumption of the path building process by keeping less paths in memory at the same time.
    Author:
    Steven Arzt
